name: Selective Nights
description:
SELECTIVE NIGHTS is about bringing culture and music together - creating something fresh for the Oslo nightlife. 

Hosted by Monsieur Dukuly, with DJ sets from FAFO and Big T, and a live performance by Mabira. 
We’re also bringing something extra: tooth gems on site by Eternal Echo. This night is about showcasing a new kind of experience different from what you’re used to. Expect new vibes, new energy, and a carefully curated atmosphere. We want to give our audience something special, and we hope you enjoy this night with us. 

Come support your locals.
